quest.name: I'll Fish It Myself
journal:
The Last Dregs is looking to resolve a fishy situation.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
Deliver the requested materials to the all-purpose service unit.
objectives: Mine [Error] from the Elysian seas.Deliver [Error] to the all-purpose service unit.Gather [Error] from the Elysian seas.Catch [Error] from the Elysian seas.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: The café is currently experiencing difficulties regarding fish-based foodstuffs. Methods of acquisition remain suboptimal and capable personnel shortages persist. To this end, staff has initiated a cultivation protocol to secure piscatory supply lines.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: Testing of various feeds for aquaculture are presently underway. Your assistance is required to seek out additional materials.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: When you are prepared, please provide bryophyte samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: When you are prepared, please provide seaweed samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text:
When you are prepared, please provide stickleback samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit. Purchase of gold salmon roe from unit
N-0598 is strongly advised.

dialogue.name: OMICRON04617
dialogue.text: Scanning inventory... <whirr> No aquaculture feed samples detected. Awaiting delivery of acceptable samples.

dialogue.name: OMICRON04617
dialogue.text: Scanning inventory... <whirr> Potential aquaculture feed samples detected. Please insert samples to continue.

dialogue.name: OMICRON04617
dialogue.text: Scanning samples... Nutritional levels acceptable. Please report to Stigma-4 for compensation.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: Report from the all-purpose service unit received. Your contributions are greatly appreciated.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: Extrapolating outcomes based on success of cultivation protocol... Should the café become reliably and adequately stocked with fish-based foodstuffs, Grebuloffs are predicted to experience the highest growth in satisfaction levels.

dialogue.name: STIGMA4
dialogue.text: Aquaculture testing will resume shortly. Please stand by and await further instructions.
